{
  "stem": "15768.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so there was always a slice of bread and jam if we--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our family spoke French at all times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, this was a given.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My, my mother was not really terribly good at it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My brother managed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he had an accent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my father and I were generally pushed to the forefront, because we were the two linguists.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we spoke to the farmers and whatever authorities or anybody who might be coming along and questioning what was going on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, absolutely, oh, absolutely-- I mean, not only hiding our identity, but staying out of sight and to avoid any kind of contact or confrontation, even with the French, with other French farmers in the area.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was all farm land.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we, under no circumstance, did we want to create difficulties for our host farmer.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because he might have been reported to the Germans for harboring refugees and thusly get into difficulties, as, as everyone did, really, who-- along the way everywhere, anybody who helped Jewish refugees was-- they were always endangering their own lives.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were certainly very aware of that implication by all means.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was a busy existence.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And yet, in a, in a sense, it was a healthy existence.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because it was a farm and fresh air and such a relief not to be behind barbed wire or locked up in some dirty hall of some sort or another without facilities and so forth.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was-- and it was a favorable time of the year it was July, which is very pleasant on the northern coast of France.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- We'll stop here and change tape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fine.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
